✅ Step 1: Download TikTok App

Install TikTok from:

Google Play Store (Android)
App Store (iPhone)
✅ Step 2: Sign Up Account

Open TikTok → Tap “Sign Up”

You can create account using:

Phone number (recommended for marketing)
Email (best for business use)
Google / Facebook (not recommended for long-term CPA work)

👉 Best option: Use a new Gmail + phone number (for safety & scaling multiple accounts)

✅ Step 3: Set Basic Profile

After signup:

Username → Keep it niche-based
👉 Example: HealthyTipsDaily, GadgetDealsHub
Profile Photo → Use:
Logo OR
Clean niche-related image

Bio → Add simple CTA:

🔥 Best Health Tips Daily
👇 Check Link Below
✅ Step 4: Switch to Business Account

Go to:
Profile → Menu → Settings → Manage Account → Switch to Business Account

Why?

Analytics access
Ad options
More credibility
✅ Step 5: Add Link (Important for CPA)

TikTok doesn’t allow links immediately.

You need:

1,000 followers OR
Use Business Account (some regions allow early link)

👉 Alternative:
Use:

Linktree
Or your own landing page (best option)

Since you're a Laravel dev → create your own landing page (HIGHLY recommended)

✅ Step 6: Content Strategy for CPA Marketing

Don’t post random videos. Focus on:

🔥 1. Problem → Solution Videos

Example:

“Struggling with breathing? Try this…”
“This product helps lungs in 7 days!”
🔥 2. Short Viral Videos
10–30 seconds
Hook in first 3 seconds
Add subtitles
🔥 3. CTA (Call To Action)

Always say:

“Check link in bio”
“Visit website now”


✅ Step 7: Use Multiple Accounts (Scaling)

For CPA marketing:

Create 2–5 TikTok accounts
Different IP / device if scaling big
Different niche per account
⚠️ Important Rules (Avoid Ban)

TikTok is strict:

❌ Don’t:

Post direct affiliate links
Spam same video
Use fake claims (“100% cure”)

✅ Do:

Use landing page
Add value content
Warm up account (watch videos first)
